---
title: Korean BBQ-Inspired Beef Bowls with Charred Veggies
description: Korean BBQ flavours in 20 min! What's the secret? Fully cooked pulled beef cuts kitchen time in half! Fluffy jasmine rice, broiled peppers, scallions and quick-pickled cucumbers make the perfect toppers.
